        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Bangkok/scene_zika.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 9d4e194d-67e5-48a6-819e-172556f40157).Image",
        "Description": "[Transmission En-Route for Agent ID: 47 ]\r\rAbiatti&apos;s personal files have revealed that he was in contact with two fledgling providence operatives via a burner phone that made calls traceable to Bangkok.\r\rWe only found out after you&apos;d left Bangkok yourself, but we&apos;d overlooked one Mrs Mookjai, along with her lover and triggerman Bob. Both are doing their best to be noticed by Providence and taken into the fold. \r\rWell, we can&apos;t allow that now can we? \r\r\r-D\r\r((This is  hard mode))",
